{"type":"question","id":318,"title":"关于新蛤社app的设计","uid":297,"topics":[467,982],"contents":"众所周知，微博的膜法文章经常被续。所以现在有必要制作一个用于备份和方便膜蛤的地方。<br>\n<br>\n我也关注到在去年Naco Siren(github)发布过一款膜法指南，不过似乎已经停更并且github上的release也不见了。所以我想整合一下旧的膜法素材，加入一些新鲜血液，并且方便广大蛤丝。<br>\n<br>\n目前框架已经搭得差不多了，请大家出出主意，江app变得更吼，谢谢。每个人都可以提建议哦。<br>\n<br>\n经好几百个教授的一致钦点后，app命名为膜盒。<br>\n<br>\nsd卡权限可以选择不给，上传图片不需要权限，下载图片要。但是考虑到app的行程，大家觉得要不要一开始就申请sd卡权限呢？<br>\n<br>\napp暂定于6月初公测，敬请期待。<br>\n<br>\n目前状况： <br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/questions/20180503/bd4539049b0029f0ab474606d7b0470a.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/questions/20180503/bd4539049b0029f0ab474606d7b0470a.png\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/questions/20180503/bd4539049b0029f0ab474606d7b0470a.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/questions/20180503/f8f1a793279013a6d383a6852508562b.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/questions/20180503/f8f1a793279013a6d383a6852508562b.png\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/questions/20180503/f8f1a793279013a6d383a6852508562b.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/questions/20180503/51a693c4e73594bc85442b702ad88127.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/questions/20180503/51a693c4e73594bc85442b702ad88127.png\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/questions/20180503/51a693c4e73594bc85442b702ad88127.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2018-04-07","agreeCount":4,"discussionCount":0}